              <h2>How this stone calculator works</h2>
              <p>
                This stone calculator estimates how much crushed stone, gravel,
                river rock, or decorative rock you need based on the area you
                want to cover, the depth of the stone layer, and the material
                density.
              </p>
              <p>
                It supports multiple shapes (rectangles, circles, borders/paths,
                and custom volumes) and gives results in
                <strong
                  >cubic feet, cubic yards, cubic meters, tons, kilograms, and
                  pounds</strong
                >.
